<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Document</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/index.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/reset.css">
  <!--jquery  -->
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include("part/_header") %>
    <main class="request">
      <section class="request-info">
        <h2 class="title text-center">제작문의</h2>
        <div class="box-grid">
          <div class="box">
            <div class="d-flex box-inner f-column">
              <div class="box-title">
                <h3>주소</h3>
                <span class="ic-map2"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="box-content">
                <div>서울시 송파구 문정동 85번지 어은회관 지하 1층</div>
                <a href="" class="d-flex ai-center gap-8">지도에서 보기
                  <span class="ic-rightsm"></span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="box">
            <div class="d-flex box-inner f-column">
              <div class="box-title">
                <h3>대표 전화</h3>
                <span class="ic-mobile"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="box-content">
                <div>010-3759-4011</div>
                <a href="" class="d-flex ai-center gap-8">전화 문의하기
                  <span class="ic-rightsm"></span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="box">
            <div class="d-flex box-inner f-column">
              <div class="box-title">
                <h3>이메일</h3>
                <span class="ic-mail"></span>
              </div>
              <div class="box-content">
                <div>ask15@naver.com</div>
                <a href="" class="d-flex ai-center gap-8">이메일 문의하기
                  <span class="ic-rightsm"></span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="request-form">
        <h3>아래 양식을 통해 내용을 등록해주시면, 빠르게 연락드리도록 하겠습니다.</h3>
        <div class="request-form-wrap">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="form-item">
              <label for="firstName">이름</label>
              <div class="input-wrap"><input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" placeholder="이름을 입력해주세요.">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-item">
              <label for="lastName">성</label>
              <div class="input-wrap"><input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" placeholder="성을 입력해주세요."></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="form-item">
              <label for="phone">휴대폰 번호</label>
              <div class="input-wrap"><input type="text" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="휴대폰 번호를 입력해주세요."></div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-item">
              <label for="email">이메일 주소</label>
              <div class="input-wrap"><input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="이메일 주소를 입력해주세요."></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-item">
            <label for="message">문의내용</label>
            <div class="textarea-wrap">
              <textarea name="message" id="message" placeholder="문의내용을 입력해주세요." maxlength="1000"></textarea>
              <div class="textarea-count"><span>0</span>/ 1,000</div>
            </div>
            <button class="submit-btn btn btn-lg btn-black">제출하기</button>
          </div>
          <div class="submit-popup-overlay ">
            <div class="submit-popup">
              <h3>제출완료</h3>
              <div class="submit-popup-inner">
                <div class="submit-popup-content">
                  <p class="submit-popup-text text-center">
                    문의내용이 등록되었습니다.<br>
                    빠른 시일 내에 연락드리겠습니다</p>
                  <button class="submit-popup-btn btn btn-md btn-black">확인</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="oneline">
          <div class="ask-text">카카오톡으로 언제든지 쉽고 빠르게 문의가 가능합니다</div>
          <a href="" class="btn-lg btn-border ask-kakao pdl-60">카카오톡 문의</a>
        </div>
      </section>
      <%- include("part/_footer") %>
    </main>

</body>

</html>

<script src="./js/index.js" type="text/javascript"></script>